          built with Rust (Axum), PostgreSQL, and FFmpeg.

          Key features:
          - Blockchain payment via X402Splitter.sol smart contract.
            Revenue split: 90% to creator, 10% to platform admin.
          - Multi-provider fiat payment plugins: Stripe, PayPal,
            Midtrans, Xendit — with automatic webhook processing.
          - Xendit auto-disburse: 90% automatically transferred to
            creator's bank account (BCA, BNI, BRI, Mandiri, etc.)
            via Xendit Disbursements API.
          - Dynamic watermarking (per-viewer, moving overlay) for
            piracy protection.
          - HLS adaptive bitrate transcoding (240p / 360p / 480p)
            via FFmpeg with hardware acceleration support.
          - HMAC-SHA256 signed session cookies (secure, httponly).
          - Admin dashboard: fiat invoice monitoring, manual disburse
            trigger, SMTP email configuration.
          - SMTP email notifications: password reset, change-password
            confirmation (lettre + Tokio async).
          - User and admin change-password with email alert.
          - Testnet support: Mega Testnet, Polygon Amoy, Sepolia.
